## Getting Started

```bash
# Install all dependencies
bun install

# Run both API and web in development
bun run dev

# Or run individually
bun run dev:api
bun run dev:web
```

## Available Scripts

```bash
bun run dev          # Start all packages in dev mode
bun run build        # Build all packages
bun run test         # Run all tests
bun run typecheck    # Type check all packages
bun run lint         # Lint all packages
bun run check        # Run all checks (typecheck + lint + test)
```

## Packages

### @<%= projectName %>/api

Backend API built with <%= apiFramework %>.

- Port: `3001` (default)
- Endpoints:
  - `GET /health` - Health check
  - `GET /api` - API info
  - `POST /api/messages` - Create message

### @<%= projectName %>/web

Frontend built with <%= webFramework %>.

- Port: `5173` (Vite) or `3000` (Next.js)
- Connects to API at `http://localhost:3001`
